<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nature Quotes</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #e6f2e6;
            color: #2d4739;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2e8b57;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #3b6b4c;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .quote {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-left: 5px solid #4CAF50;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .author {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Hello World!</h1>
    <h2>Learn here, lead anywhere... Salma</h2>

    <div class="quote">
        "Look deep into nature, and then you will understand everything better."
        <div class="author">– Albert Einstein</div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
        "In every walk with nature one receives far more than he seeks."
        <div class="author">– John Muir</div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
        "The earth has music for those who listen."
        <div class="author">– William Shakespeare</div>
    </div>

    <div class="quote">
        "Adopt the pace of nature: her secret is patience."
        <div class="author">– Ralph Waldo Emerson</div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
